data.description: Welcome home to this large single story 4 bedroom 3 bath nestled in Spring Trails situated just a 4 minute walk from Broadway Elementary.  If you enjoy privacy, you'll enjoy having no neighbors on one side next to the nature area that cannot be developed.  The home boasts a large entry hallway that is wide and open.  The Guest Bedroom has a full bathroom ensuite with a large closet as well.  Secondary bedrooms both have walk-in closets.  The media room currently serves as a children's playroom for rainy days or hot summers, but has also been used as a private office.  The formal dining room is just steps from the open kitchen and living room/family room, and the breakfast area is large enough to accomodate a traditional dinner table.  All wall treatments are custom ordered removable luxury wallpaper so it can easily be removed if not to your liking!
